description:
Season: 19
Original Air Date: 12/15/2005

Stephanie becomes curious to the reason for Eric’s sudden change of heart, however Eric just says that it has taken him some time to realize all of this.  Then when the conversation shifts to their children, Eric realizes that Felicia has a son.  Bridget is stunned and a bit upset by the fact that Nick has had a child with Felicia.  The two of them visit Felicia and Bridget is introduced to baby Dominick.
